<section class="page-hero page-hero--compact">
  <div class="container split split--about-grid">
    <div class="about-intro">
      <p class="eyebrow reveal" data-reveal>About</p>
      <h1 class="display display--sm reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 40ms">A brokerage built on integrity and process</h1>
      <p class="muted reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 80ms">
        <strong>Sood Mortgages Group</strong> operates as a mortgage brokerage serving clients who value straight answers, organized paperwork, and a partner who respects the other professionals on your transaction — agents, attorneys, CPAs, and builders.
      </p>
    </div>
    <figure class="about-photo media-frame reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 80ms" data-parallax="subtle">
      <img
        src="<%= images.aboutOffice %>"
        alt="Bright professional office interior — corporate mortgage advisory environment"
        width="1200"
        height="900"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </figure>
    <div class="about-visual card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 120ms" data-parallax="subtle">
      <p class="panel-kicker">Corporate &amp; professional</p>
      <p class="muted">
        Our visual identity follows a mono minimal standard: high contrast, restrained typography, and motion that supports reading — never distraction. That mirrors how we approach your loan file.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container split">
    <div class="reveal" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="section-title">Principles we hold constant</h2>
      <ul class="values-list">
        <li><strong>Transparency</strong> — you see the same numbers and narratives we share with lenders.</li>
        <li><strong>Compliance</strong> — disclosures and timing follow regulatory expectations without shortcuts.</li>
        <li><strong>Respect for your time</strong> — we batch questions and document requests instead of dripping them across weeks.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 70ms">
      <h3 class="h3">Who we serve best</h3>
      <p class="muted">
        Buyers who want a broker who can translate lender jargon, homeowners weighing a refinance against other financial goals, and investors who need file discipline across multiple properties. If you prefer a high-pressure sales floor, we are likely not the right fit — and we are comfortable saying so.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--muted">
  <div class="container split split--flip split--flip-reverse">
    <figure class="media-frame reveal" data-reveal data-parallax="subtle">
      <img
        src="<%= images.aboutTeam %>"
        alt="Mortgage professionals collaborating — advisory team environment"
        width="800"
        height="800"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </figure>
    <div class="reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 50ms">
      <p class="eyebrow">Advisory team</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Experience across purchase, refi, and portfolio files</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        <strong>Sood Mortgages Group</strong> brings a corporate mortgage mindset to every relationship: disciplined checklists, respectful communication, and a bias toward documentation that survives investor audit — whether you are buying your first home or refinancing a rental you have owned for a decade.
      </p>
      <p class="muted">
        We coordinate with your real estate agent on timeline-sensitive milestones and keep attorneys or CPAs in the loop when tax returns, entity documents, or trust structures are part of the story.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="section-title">Why a broker channel matters in today’s rate environment</h2>
      <p class="muted narrow-inline">Wholesale and correspondent access can widen pricing and program choice — with one accountable partner coordinating the file.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-row">
      <div class="stat-card card reveal" data-reveal>
        <p class="stat-value">Multi-lender</p>
        <p class="muted small">Compare scenarios without managing five different portals on your own.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 40ms">
        <p class="stat-value">Plain language</p>
        <p class="muted small">Written summaries you can forward to family or advisors before you lock.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card card reveal" data-reveal style="--delay: 80ms">
        <p class="stat-value">Process-first</p>
        <p class="muted small">Underwriting readiness baked in — fewer fire drills before closing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--dark">
  <div class="container cta-band reveal" data-reveal>
    <div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Want to verify fit before you share documents?</h2>
      <p class="muted">Start with a short consultation — no obligation, no scripted pitch.</p>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/contact">Reach out</a>
  </div>
</section>
